---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Technosworld — Built from Kutus, built for Kenya"
	description="The story behind Technosworld — why we started, what we stand for, and where we're going."
>
	<!-- Page Hero -->
	<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-navy">
		<img
			src="/images/about/team-at-work.jpg"
			alt="Technosworld team at work"
			class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover object-center"
		/>
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-navy/65 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
		<div class="reveal relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-24 md:px-10 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
			<p class="eyebrow mb-4 text-white/70">Our story</p>
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-white md:text-5xl">
				Built from Kutus.<br />Built for Kenya.
			</h1>
			<p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-white/80">
				A technology company that started by asking why Kenyan businesses
				have to settle for less — and decided to do something about it.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Our Story -->
	<section class="bg-white">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-20 md:px-10 md:py-28">
			<div class="reveal mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
				<p class="eyebrow mb-4">Where we came from</p>
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy md:text-4xl">Three conversations that built a company</h2>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-16 flex flex-col gap-20">
				<!-- Story 1 -->
				<div class="reveal flex flex-col items-center gap-10 md:flex-row md:gap-16">
					<div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center md:w-2/5">
						<div class="h-48 w-48 overflow-hidden rounded-full border-4 border-surface shadow-xl">
							<img src="/images/about/restaurant-owner.png" alt="Restaurant owner" class="h-full w-full object-cover" />
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="w-full md:w-3/5">
						<p class="eyebrow mb-3">How it started</p>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy">The restaurant owner who was invisible online</h3>
						<p class="mt-4 text-charcoal">
							We spent a morning with the owner of a popular restaurant in Kutus — the kind of place that fills up on Friday nights and buzzes the whole day on Sunday. She had no website. She managed reservations through a personal WhatsApp group that had more forwarded voice notes than actual booking requests. When we searched for her restaurant online, nothing came up.
						</p>
						<p class="mt-4 text-charcoal">
							A smaller, quieter competitor two streets away had a basic website and was appearing in every local Google search. She was losing customers she would never even know about — people who searched, found nothing, and walked somewhere else.
						</p>
						<p class="mt-4 text-charcoal">
							We asked how many businesses she knew in the same position. She said: almost everyone.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Story 2 -->
				<div class="reveal flex flex-col items-center gap-10 md:flex-row-reverse md:gap-16">
					<div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center md:w-2/5">
						<div class="h-48 w-48 overflow-hidden rounded-full border-4 border-surface shadow-xl">
							<img src="/images/about/paper-ledger.png" alt="Business ledger" class="h-full w-full object-cover" />
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="w-full md:w-3/5">
						<p class="eyebrow mb-3">The gap we found</p>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy">Great businesses held back by the tools available to them</h3>
						<p class="mt-4 text-charcoal">
							As we looked further, the same pattern appeared everywhere. SACCO secretaries spending two hours every morning answering balance enquiries on a phone, one member at a time, from a ledger written in two different people's handwriting. Clinic receptionists managing appointment books across two competing notebooks, creating double-bookings every week. Hardware shops tracking stock on paper that got wet in the rains.
						</p>
						<p class="mt-4 text-charcoal">
							These were not failing businesses. They were well-run, trusted, profitable operations — held back by the gap between the digital tools available to large companies in Nairobi and the practical reality of building an SME in Kirinyaga County.
						</p>
						<p class="mt-4 text-charcoal">
							Affordable, professional digital tools existed — but they were built for markets that looked nothing like Kenya. They assumed fast internet, credit card payments, English-only users, and IT teams to manage them. None of those assumptions held here.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Story 3 -->
				<div class="reveal flex flex-col items-center gap-10 md:flex-row md:gap-16">
					<div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center md:w-2/5">
						<div class="h-48 w-48 overflow-hidden rounded-full border-4 border-surface shadow-xl">
							<img src="/images/about/tech-partnership.png" alt="Tech partnership" class="h-full w-full object-cover" />
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="w-full md:w-3/5">
						<p class="eyebrow mb-3">Why we built Technosworld</p>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy">A permanent partner, not another vendor</h3>
						<p class="mt-4 text-charcoal">
							We didn't want to be another freelancer who builds a website and disappears when the maintenance becomes complicated. We didn't want to be a Nairobi agency charging rates that assume a Westlands budget and sending a consultant who has never been to Kirinyaga to "understand your needs."
						</p>
						<p class="mt-4 text-charcoal">
							Technosworld exists to be the permanent digital partner for businesses across Kenya — close enough to understand your market, skilled enough to build enterprise-quality systems, and honest about what your business actually needs versus what would look good on our portfolio.
						</p>
						<p class="mt-4 font-semibold text-navy">
							We are being built for the long term, from Kutus, for Africa.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- What We Stand For -->
	<section class="bg-surface">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-20 md:px-10 md:py-28">
			<div class="reveal mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
				<p class="eyebrow mb-4">Our principles</p>
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy md:text-4xl">What we stand for</h2>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
				<div class="card reveal">
					<div class="mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-navy/5">
						<svg class="h-6 w-6 text-navy" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">Purpose-built for Kenya</h3>
					<p class="mt-3 text-charcoal">
						We don't copy-paste solutions built for London or Silicon Valley. We design systems around M-Pesa, Safaricom SMS, WhatsApp Business, and the realities of doing business in East Africa — from the network speeds to the languages to the payment habits.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="card reveal">
					<div class="mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-navy/5">
						<svg class="h-6 w-6 text-navy" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">The long view, not the quick job</h3>
					<p class="mt-3 text-charcoal">
						We measure our success in years, not invoices. We stick around — training your team, updating your systems as your business changes, and responding when something breaks. Your growth is what keeps us in business.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="card reveal">
					<div class="mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-navy/5">
						<svg class="h-6 w-6 text-navy" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">Straight-talking on cost</h3>
					<p class="mt-3 text-charcoal">
						We tell you the price before we start, explain every component, and don't charge extra when you need another revision. No hidden maintenance fees. No surprise invoices. No rate that suddenly doubles once we're midway through a project.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Stats -->
	<section class="bg-white">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-20 md:px-10 md:py-28">
			<div class="reveal mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
				<p class="eyebrow mb-4">By the numbers</p>
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy md:text-4xl">Where we are today</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
				<div class="reveal text-center">
					<p class="text-5xl font-bold text-navy">5</p>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm font-bold text-charcoal">Core services</p>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Websites, software, AI tools, infrastructure, and branding — delivered by one team with no handoffs.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="reveal text-center">
					<p class="text-5xl font-bold text-navy">1st</p>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm font-bold text-charcoal">Starting in Kirinyaga</p>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">We started where we could serve best — Kutus and Kirinyaga County — before expanding across Kenya.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="reveal text-center">
					<p class="text-5xl font-bold text-navy">5+</p>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm font-bold text-charcoal">Sectors we serve</p>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Restaurants, SACCOs, hospitals, clubs, and general SMEs — each with purpose-built solutions.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="reveal text-center">
					<p class="text-5xl font-bold text-navy">1</p>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm font-bold text-charcoal">Live SaaS product</p>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">TechpointPOS — our point-of-sale platform already serving Kenyan retailers before Technosworld launched.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- TechpointPOS -->
	<section class="bg-surface">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-20 md:px-10 md:py-28">
			<div class="reveal mx-auto max-w-4xl">
				<div class="card flex flex-col gap-6 md:flex-row md:items-center md:gap-12">
					<div class="flex-1">
						<p class="eyebrow mb-3">Already live</p>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy">TechpointPOS — our first shipped product</h2>
						<p class="mt-4 text-charcoal">
							Before Technosworld had a marketing site, we shipped a product. TechpointPOS is our SaaS point-of-sale platform built for Kenyan retailers — supporting electronics shops, mobile phone dealers, hardware stores, beauty and cosmetics businesses, and furniture outlets.
						</p>
						<p class="mt-3 text-charcoal">
							It handles sales, inventory, receipts, and reporting — with M-Pesa integration built in from day one. It is the proof that we don't just talk about building for Kenya; we already have.
						</p>
						<a
							href="https://www.techpointpos.co.ke/"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer"
							class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-navy-bright hover:text-navy"
						>
							Visit techpointpos.co.ke
							<svg class="h-4 w-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
							</svg>
						</a>
					</div>
					<div class="flex-shrink-0 text-center">
						<div class="inline-flex h-24 w-24 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-navy/5">
							<svg class="h-12 w-12 text-navy" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Roadmap -->
	<section class="bg-white">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-20 md:px-10 md:py-28">
			<div class="reveal mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
				<p class="eyebrow mb-4">Where we're going</p>
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy md:text-4xl">The road ahead</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 text-charcoal">We have a clear long-term vision. Today we are building the foundation.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
				<div class="card reveal border-l-4 border-l-navy-bright">
					<p class="eyebrow mb-2">Now — available today</p>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">TechnosWeb & TechnosReach</h3>
					<p class="mt-3 text-charcoal">Professional websites and digital branding services — already available for businesses in Kirinyaga County and beyond. This is where we start: making your business visible and professional online.</p>
					<a href="/#services" class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-bold text-navy-bright hover:text-navy">
						See our services
						<svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg>
					</a>
				</div>

				<div class="card reveal">
					<p class="eyebrow mb-2 text-muted">Coming next</p>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">TechnosCore, TechnosMind & TechnosPay</h3>
					<p class="mt-3 text-charcoal">Management software, AI-powered business tools, and a payments infrastructure product — built specifically for East African SMEs. These are under development and will be available as Technosworld grows.</p>
					<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">Interested in early access? <a href="/contact" class="font-bold text-navy-bright hover:text-navy">Get in touch.</a></p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- CTA -->
	<section class="bg-navy">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-20 text-center md:px-10">
			<div class="reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow mb-4 text-white/60">Work with us</p>
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white md:text-4xl">Ready to work with a team built for the long term?</h2>
				<p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-white/70">
					Based in Kutus, Kirinyaga County. Serving businesses across Kenya and East Africa. No commitment required for the first conversation.
				</p>
				<div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
					<a href="/contact" class="btn-primary bg-white text-navy hover:bg-surface">Get in touch</a>
					<a href="/#services" class="btn-outline border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-navy">See our services</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
